{"tid":1474495,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"【極重要！斷網絡拆解】熱門竟然無呢個APP？！","createTime":"2019-08-15T07:55:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T15:27:52.000Z","uid":93536,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"1106a4e871ac26bd222abc0886ac7325230e4f5b","tid":1474495,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:55:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://buzzorange.com/techorange/2019/08/13/bridgefy-and-hongkong/?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com%2Ftechorange%2F2019%2F08%2F13%2Fbridgefy-and-hongkong%2F%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdtXdGXproJJDEW77mXnEmng%3D&h=40b23a63\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://buzzorange.com/techorange/2019/08/13/bridgefy-and-hongkong/?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">網路被切斷也不怕！香港人狂推沒網路也能傳訊的超強 App： <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">Bridgefy</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">Bridgefy 有 4 種使用模式，能因應沒網路的「非常時期」</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>(1) 人-人模式（PERSON TO PERSON MODE）</strong><br />\n<br />\n在這種模式下，只要打開藍牙就能與距離使用者不到 100 公尺的朋友進行私聊。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>(2) 網狀網路模式（MESH MODE）</strong><br />\n<br />\n在 MESH MODE 下，可以透過中間點（另一名 Bridgefy 使用者）與超過 100 公尺以外的朋友聊天，也就是呈現【人 1-人 2-人 3】的傳訊模式，使可能通訊距離達到 200 公尺， 人 1 與人 3 之間的訊息將維持私密性，人 2 是無法閱讀其訊息的。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>(3) 廣播模式（BROADCAST MODE）</strong><br />\n<br />\n在廣播模式下，使用者可以同時向周圍所有使用 Bridgefy 的人發送訊息，即使這些人並不在聯絡人列表中。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>(4) 線上模式（ONLINE MODE）</strong><br />\n<br />\n除了這三種模式以外，Bridgefy 也有 online 模式可以使用，可以透過網路連接到所有有使用 Bridgefy ，並同樣是以網路連線的朋友們。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">快撚啲同我Down哂佢！推呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"050d5be5ae4757d9cceb465b1fd49c14c6b8a03a","tid":1474495,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:56:11.000Z","msg":"自推十連發開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"730e83c3a2fd7b2ea80ee26072734fa40db0fa00","tid":1474495,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:56:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9caa152b3087f082a52c150561817a20dc3e0b19","tid":1474495,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:56:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64833f778dae1aac847eb61f45385944aa96c7bd","tid":1474495,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:57:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"848fc6d94a72725e7069238c71673011f4dffbf0","tid":1474495,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:57:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30854d8ec2fda5279415de9d7504e337db756c0d","tid":1474495,"uid":93536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c31787b4c92f7ed4d8d8a93505a730a3f07011